import React from 'react'
import {Form, Button, Modal} from "react-bootstrap";

function QuestionAddModal({numberOfQuest, show}) {
    
    return (
        <Modal
            size="lg"
            aria-labelledby="contained-modal-title-vcenter"
            centered

        >
            <Modal.Header>
                <Modal.Title id="contained-modal-title-vcenter">
                    Thêm câu hỏi (câu {numberOfQuest + 1})
                </Modal.Title>
            </Modal.Header>
            <Modal.Body>
                
            </Modal.Body>
            <Modal.Footer>
            <Button variant="outline-success">Thêm</Button>
            </Modal.Footer>
        </Modal>
    )
}

export default QuestionAddModal
